node.text: I spent some time in Italy this past month! And now back to rainy/windy Brighton. Yesterday I got to see some of my @mai_accents ceramics stocked in a shop in Brighton, for the first time - you can find them @thepopupclub_ if you wanna see them popping out here and there as you shop. 😉 ALSO, Hokusai x @tsuki_market also launched recently!! 🌊 Hope you are all having a nice summer. ☺️

node.text:
🌟 2 0 2 1 🎉
I hope everyone is feeling excited for the new year, but most importantly is safe and well. I’ve loved sharing my journey with everyone that decided to follow it throughout the years; it’s been great, and it has allowed me to grow and connect with people all over the world. This is something I truly value, but I have been ready for a change and want to focus more on my life offline. I may still show up from time to time, just don’t be alarmed by the fact that it won’t be as much. I thank you all for sticking with me and for the support you’ve given me. Happy New Year! ❤️
